{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles\"><strong>WAI-ARIA roles</strong></a>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/button_role\"><code>Using the button role</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/List_role\"><code>ARIA: list role</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/listbox_role\"><code>ARIA: listbox role</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Listitem_role\"><code>ARIA: listitem role</code></a></li></ol>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>此页面列出了涵盖 MDN 上讨论的所有 WAI-ARIA 角色的参考页面。有关角色的完整列表，请参阅 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques\">ARIA 技术</a></p><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"aria_list_role\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/List_role\">ARIA: list role</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">ARIA <code>list</code> 角色可用于标识项目列表。它通常与 <code>listitem</code> 角色结合使用，该角色用于标识包含在列表中的列表项。</dd><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"aria_listbox_role\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/listbox_role\">ARIA: listbox role</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\"><code>listbox</code> 角色用于列表，用户可以从中选择一个或多个静态选项，并且与 HTML <code>select</code> 元素不同，它可能包含图像。</dd><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"aria_listitem_role\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Listitem_role\">ARIA: listitem role</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">ARIA <code>listitem</code> 角色可用于标识项目列表中的项目。它通常与 <code>list</code> 角色结合使用，用于标识列表容器。</dd><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"using_the_button_role\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/button_role\">Using the button role</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/roles#button\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">button</a></strong> 角色应该用于可单击的元素，当用户激活时触发响应。在其本身，<code>role=\"button\"</code> 可以使任何元素 (e.g. <code>p</code>, <code>span</code> or <code>div</code>) 作为一个屏幕阅读器的按钮控件出现。此外，该角色还可以与 <code>aria-pressed</code> 属性组合使用，以创建切换按钮。</dd></dl>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"此页面列出了涵盖 MDN 上讨论的所有 WAI-ARIA 角色的参考页面。有关角色的完整列表，请参阅 ARIA 技术","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA ロール","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/accessibility/aria/roles","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/accessibility/aria/roles/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"无障碍"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles","title":"WAI-ARIA Roles"}],"pageTitle":"WAI-ARIA Roles - 无障碍 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}